lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Spaniard Garbine Muguruza was knocked out in the second round of the U.S. Open on Wednesday in a shocking 7-5 6-4 upset by 48th-ranked Anastasija Sevastova of Latvia.

headline.print_headline: Muguruza Crashes Out of U.S. Open in Second Round
